Point-LIO: expose a coherent point-time-deskewed lidar snapshot.

The estimator already registers each filter_size_surf-downsampled point group
with the state at that group's sensor time in feats_down_world. Preserve those
endpoints, but express them in the lidar frame at the final processed group so
the existing cloud-plus-odometry transport contract remains usable. This
snapshot remains filter_size_surf-downsampled; it is not a world-frame
registered_scan. Keep the existing body-cloud API unchanged, and surface
whether a process call consumed a new scan; callers must not infer this from a
retained last result.

